            <title>
                <![CDATA[京東開啓蘋果年貨節：力度比官網更大，iPhone 15 機型 5199 元起]]>
            </title>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p data-vmark="ebc4"><a class="s_tag" href="https://www.ithome.com/" target="_blank">IT 之家</a> 1 月 16 日消息，蘋果中國官網上線官降活動，將於 1 月 18 日-21 日開啓「迎新春限時優惠」，參與產品包括手機、電腦、平板、手錶、耳機以及 Apple Pencil，其中&nbsp;<a class="s_tag" href="https://iphone.ithome.com/" target="_blank">iPhone</a>&nbsp;15 系列降價 500 元、MacBook Air 降 800 元。</p><p data-vmark="3b46">隨後，京東宣佈開啓「<a href="https://union-click.jd.com/jdc?e=&amp;" target="_blank" data-wapurl="https://union-click.jd.com/jdc?e=&amp;" data-iosurl="https://union-click.jd.com/jdc?e=&amp;" data-androidurl="https://union-click.jd.com/jdc?e=&amp;" data-uwpurl="https://union-click.jd.com/jdc?e=&amp;" data-wxmpurl="ithome://openmp?appid=wx91d27dbf599dff74&amp;path=%2fpages%2funion%2fproxy%2fproxy%3fspreadUrl%3dhttps%253a%252f%252funion-click.jd.com%252fjdc%253fe%253d%2526p%%26EA_PTAG%3d17078.27.380">蘋果年貨節</a>」，<strong><a class="s_tag" href="https://iphone.ithome.com/" target="_blank">iPhone 15</a>&nbsp;系列直降 800 元，比官網多便宜 300 元，</strong><a class="s_tag" href="https://iphone.ithome.com/" target="_blank">iPhone 15 Pro</a>&nbsp;和 Pro Max 也直降 600 元，<a class="s_tag" href="https://iphone.ithome.com/" target="_blank">iPhone 14</a>&nbsp;直降 700 元。</p><p data-vmark="7a8d" style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2024/1/f2e9d794-bc0f-4756-b672-fe1820da1829.jpg?x-bce-process=image/format,f_auto" w="1125" h="2523" title="京東開啓蘋果年貨節：力度比官網更大，iPhone 15 機型 5199 元起" width="1125" height="1839" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></p><p data-vmark="0259" style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2024/1/2dcc8696-99c6-4ca6-934c-be80aff2792f.jpg?x-bce-process=image/format,f_auto" w="1125" h="2523" title="京東開啓蘋果年貨節：力度比官網更大，iPhone 15 機型 5199 元起" width="1125" height="1839" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></p><p data-vmark="0f45">IT 之家注意到，<a class="s_tag" href="https://ipad.ithome.com/" target="_blank">iPad</a>、MacBook、Apple Watch 等產品的折扣力度也比官網更大。其中，iPad 至高優惠 700 元，MacBook Air 至高優惠 800 元，Apple Watch S9 至高優惠 450 元，AirPods 限時優惠 100 元。</p><p data-vmark="65b3" style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2024/1/ba6a1375-1c23-4af1-bba1-32da2b366d3c.jpg?x-bce-process=image/format,f_auto" w="1125" h="3955" title="京東開啓蘋果年貨節：力度比官網更大，iPhone 15 機型 5199 元起" width="1125" height="2883" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></p><p data-vmark="d8cc" style="text-align: left;"><strong>相關閲讀</strong></p><p data-vmark="ccc6" style="text-align: left;">《<a href="https://www.ithome.com/0/745/214.htm" target="_blank">蘋果中國上線迎新春限時活動：iPhone 15 系列手機最高降 500 元，Mac、iPad 也有優惠</a>》</p><dir><a contenteditable="false" href="https://u.jd.com/lz4UT6O" target="_blank" data-wapurl="https://u.jd.com/li4R4v9" data-iosurl="https://u.jd.com/li4cph2" data-androidurl="https://u.jd.com/lb4jmzZ" data-hosurl="https://u.jd.com/lu4c4eT" data-uwpurl="https://u.jd.com/ls4cpbD" data-wxmpurl="ithome://openmp?appid=wx91d27dbf599dff74&amp;path=%2fpages%2funion%2fproxy%2fproxy%3fspreadUrl%3dhttps%253a%252f%252fu.jd.com%252flz4UTlZ%26EA_PTAG%3d17078.27.380" data-itwxurl="https://u.jd.com/lz4HfPf" data-lpwxurl="https://u.jd.com/lq4f8W5" data-jdid="100066896214"><span class="card main-site"><span class="card-logo"><img src="https://img14.360buyimg.com/pop/jfs/t1/59220/8/26333/45934/65a1271eF730a2de4/976d20558bfe3ad8.jpg" title="京東開啓蘋果年貨節：力度比官網更大，iPhone 15 機型 5199 元起" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="card-info"><span class="card-title"><span class="mall-data">京東</span><span class="card-name">蘋果 iPhone 15 128GB</span></span><span class="card-abstract"></span><span class="card-controls"><span class="price">5199 元</span><span class="card-btn-deep">直達鏈接</span></span></span></span></a></dir><dir><a contenteditable="false" href="https://u.jd.com/lq4R0ii" target="_blank" data-wapurl="https://u.jd.com/lb4ftPT" data-iosurl="https://u.jd.com/ls4c4YC" data-androidurl="https://u.jd.com/ls4cj7E" data-hosurl="https://u.jd.com/lq4XTi5" data-uwpurl="https://u.jd.com/lu47cIb" data-wxmpurl="ithome: